author: gvanmatre
msg: In preparation for cloning the shale-clay-starter-archetype (contributed by Hermod Opstvedt) to seed a shale-clay-trinidad-archetype, I've expanded the generated trinidad clay config to include the custom trinidad action listeners, converters and validators.  I also added a simple example of using the trinidad "pageFlowScope".
